edu.princeton.cs.algs4

Class AssignmentProblem

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.princeton.cs.algs4.AssignmentProblem

  • public class AssignmentProblem
extends java.lang.Object
    Compilation: javac AssignmentProblem.java Execution: java AssignmentProblem N Dependencies: DijkstraSP.java DirectedEdge.java Solve an N-by-N assignment problem in N^3 log N time using the successive shortest path algorithm. Remark: could use dense version of Dijsktra's algorithm for improved theoretical efficiency of N^3, but it doesn't seem to help in practice. Assumes N-by-N cost matrix is nonnegative.
